# Books List

This project allows you to create a book list where you can add, edit, and remove books. It utilizes DOM manipulation, local storage for persistence, and basic UI interactions.
 
## Features

- Add new books to the list.
- Remove books from the list.
- Edit book titles.
- Persist the list in local storage.

## Technologies

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Setup

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/comoartista/books.git
```
